oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Clowns outside Princess Theatre
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of several people dressed as clowns lining up outside of the Princess Theatre in Columbia, Tennessee. Two unidentified individuals (on left) hold a sign that says: "We're going to see Joe E. Brown in the 'Circus Clown' Princess Now." Similar signs promoting Joe E. Brown can be seen hanging above the theater entrance and in the lobby card cases.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Clowns; Circuses & shows; People; Theaters
